  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Remove Border Radius from Gallery Card Image Bottom\n\nUpdate the gallery card image styling to remove border radius from the bottom corners while maintaining any existing top corner radius.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the CSS class or styles for `.gallery-card-image` or equivalent image elements\n- Set `border-bottom-left-radius: 0` and `border-bottom-right-radius: 0`\n- Alternatively, use `border-radius` shorthand with top values only (e.g., `border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0`)\n- Verify the change applies to all gallery card images throughout the application\n- Ensure no override styles are preventing the change from taking effect\n- Test that top border radius (if any) remains intact",
